title: Zelensky says 31,000 Ukrainian troops have been killed since invasion
description: The figure was the first official estimate provided by Ukraine’s president on his country’s military losses during the conflict with Russia.

title: U.S. struggles for influence in West Africa as military juntas rise
description: Officials detailed their efforts to partner with the military governments in a region where Islamic extremism is surging and Russian influence expanding.

title: As Lebanon teeters on the edge, a war with Israel would be catastrophic
description: A slow moving economic disaster has hobbled Lebanon for years, making it acutely vulnerable to a potential war with Israel.

title: U.S. and U.K. carry out fresh strikes against Houthi targets in Yemen
description: It was the largest military action in weeks against the militant group, which is attacking shipping vessels to target Israel’s economy over the war in Gaza.
